# delete old kernels

cheat vkpurge

# search package repositories

xbps-query -Rs <package name>

# dependency analysis

| command                 | utility                                                               |
| ----------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| xbps-query -m           | List user-installed (explicit) packages                               |
| xbps-query -l           | List all installed packages                                           |
| xbps-query -x <package> | Show direct dependencies of a specific package                        |
| xbps-query -X <package> | Show reverse dependencies (which packages depend on this one)         |
| xbps-query -O           | List package orphans (installed as dependencies but no longer needed) |
| xilog <package>         | Show installation date                                                |
| xmandoc <manpage>       | Read manpage of possibly not installed package                        |
